| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1151 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 4d8df2da-47a1-5e85-94c3-a7e04278b031"
